 
Install python 
Install Rest_framework
install django
install Mysql

To run the project:
python manage.py runserver :
For Creating, Updating, Deleting, Posting  the books through  Rest_APi
      urls: http://127.0.0.1:8000/api/studentapi/


For Accessing the books for a Student:
      urls: http://127.0.0.1:8000





 project structure explanation:

 create a Library_Management project
   inside the project we create to app 
    first one is for Rest_framework (library)
    second one is student_view  for accesssing the books 



Note: Due to less time I can not implement login Authentication  but i tried it. 
